Usage: vcpe up --manifest <path> [flags]

Reconciles networks, images, IPAM allocation, and compose lifecycle in a single journaled operation. Alias: apply

Required flags:
  --manifest <path>       Path to deployment manifest YAML

Optional flags:
  --allow-disruptive      Permit CIDR changes and scale-to-zero operations that would otherwise be blocked
  --state-root <path>     Override the default state root directory
  --socket <path>         Override the daemon socket path
  --json                  Emit structured JSON output

Examples:
  vcpe up --manifest ./manifest-bng-7.yaml
  vcpe up --manifest ./manifest.yaml --allow-disruptive
